<https://w3id.org/2025/apso> a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:comment """APSO v0.1 — Product AAS blueprint ontology.\r
\r
  This file describes inter-submodel relations for the Product AAS blueprint.\r
  Structure is extracted from the supplied Product AAS diagram:\r
    Product(AAS)\r
      - assetInformation:AssetInformation [1]\r
      - BatchInformation:SM [1]\r
      - BoM:SM [1]\r
      - Requirements:SM [0..1]\r
      - BoP:SM [1]\r
\r
  Per-submodel modules define the internal structure of BatchInformation,\r
  BoM, Requirements and BoP. This root ontology defines typed direct links\r
  between an AssetAdministrationShell and those submodels, plus cross-submodel\r
  dependency constraints such as BoM joint references and disassembly links.""" ;
    owl:imports <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/>,
        <https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/batch-information>,
        <https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/bill-of-materials>,
        <https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/bill-of-process>,
        <https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/requirements> ;
    owl:versionIRI <https://w3id.org/2025/apso/0.1.0> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#IsDisassembleByRelationship> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:comment "Relationship from a BoM Entity to the Process or ProcessStructure that disassembles it." ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/RelationshipElement> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#hasJointParameterCollection-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:class <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#JointConnectionARE> ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#hasJointParameterCollection> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#hasSubmodel-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:class <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/AssetAdministrationShell> ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#hasSubmodel> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#isDisassembledBy-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:class <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#BomEntity> ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#isDisassembledBy> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#jointFirstEntity-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:class <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#JointConnectionARE> ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#jointFirstEntity> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#jointSecondEntity-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
