    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#jointSecondEntity> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#processOrderFirstProcess-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:class <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#ProcessOrderARE> ;
    sh:targetSubjectsOf <https://w3id.org/2025/apso#processOrderFirstProcess> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso#processOrderSecondProcess-shape> a sh:NodeShape ;
