<https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/batch-information> a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:comment "APSO module: BatchInformation submodel for Product AAS blueprint." ;
    owl:imports <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/bill-of-materials> a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:comment """APSO module: Bill of Materials submodel for Product AAS blueprint.\r
\r
This module follows the revised Product AAS diagram. The BoM contains one\r
EntryNode entity, one ArcheType string, zero or more JointConnection annotated\r
relationship elements, and zero or more JointParams collections. JointParams is\r
modeled explicitly because JointConnection.annotations/JointParamsRef points to\r
one such collection.""" ;
    owl:imports <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/bill-of-process> a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:comment """APSO module: Bill of Process submodel for Product AAS blueprint.\r
\r
This revised module follows the updated diagram and explicitly includes\r
Process, ProcessOrder and ProcessStructure. Processes is an SML that can contain\r
process strings and structured process descriptions. ProcessOrder is modeled as\r
an annotated relationship element that orders two Process entries by references.""" ;
    owl:imports <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/> .

<https://w3id.org/2025/apso/modules/requirements> a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:comment "APSO module: Requirements submodel for Product AAS blueprint." ;
    owl:imports <https://admin-shell.io/aas/3/1/> .

